{"tid":459366,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蘋果踢爆】維他奶子公司扮環保假回收 逾萬學校飯盒每日直送堆填區","createTime":"2017-11-05T16:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T23:31:12.000Z","uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"39ae0c100d17cb4bd1f5c564a11e4cff9605d9e0","tid":459366,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T16:15:16.000Z","msg":"【蘋果踢爆】維他奶子公司扮環保假回收 逾萬學校飯盒每日直送堆填區<br />\n本港逾400間學校訂購即棄飯盒，每日產生數以十萬計飯盒。《蘋果》調查發現，維他奶集團全資附屬機構香港美食有限公司，在學校收回午膳飯盒和廚餘後，直接倒入大型垃圾桶，然後由垃圾車運去廢物轉運站，估計每日涉及逾萬個飯盒棄置堆填區，違反對校方的環保承諾。香港美食辯稱是政府延遲落成廚餘廠所致，為未能銜接安排回收表示歉意。<br />\n<br />\n記者 潘柏林<br />\n<br />\n環保署在2009年起推行環保午膳，向中小學校提供無約束力的「學校推行環保午膳指引」，建議校方不要使用即棄餐盒，如要用聚丙烯餐盒，應與膳食供應商訂定妥善回收廢膠的安排。<br />\n<br />\n不過，有飯盒供應商涉及假環保，維他奶旗下的香港美食為逾百間學校提供飯盒，記者上月追蹤香港美食在元朗廠房運作，早上有車隊去各間學校派飯盒，其中一輛前往聖公會蔡功譜中學，下午貨車到學校運走飯盒。當貨車駛回廠房後，工人直接打開保溫箱，將一袋袋飯盒連廚餘掉棄到大型垃圾桶。其後有壓縮垃圾車運走飯盒和廚餘，最後駛至環保署新界西北廢物轉運站棄置。<br />\n<br />\n聖公會蔡功譜中學副校長關綺媚指，香港美食向校方介紹時，聲稱飯盒是可回收和可循環再造，但雙方簽約時，未寫入回收條款，未料對方會全數棄置，「一嚟我哋冇去監察、冇去問，所以我哋都唔知道。」仁濟醫院林百欣中學的梁老師指，香港美食回覆校方文件，在環保減廢措施稱會處理廚餘，由有一間回收商負責處理廚餘。<br />\n<br />\n香港美食回覆稱，新學年轉用新的政府認可回收商，原計劃廚餘運至小蠔灣廚餘廠，最近才接獲承辦商通知，廚餘廠延遲至明年首季啟用，公司已另覓回收商，本月初起協助過渡期間的廚餘回收，對未能即時作出銜接安排表示歉意，香港美食指近五成的餐盒及餐具是可回收重用，收回後在學校或生產工場清洗乾淨後循環再用。<br />\n<br />\n有回收業界稱，飯盒商棄置飯盒和廚餘情況非常普遍。記者在大埔太平工業中心觀察，飯盒商如帆船飲食、盈信膳食天地和嘉里物流旗下的九至五飲食，均有大批膠飯盒棄置在大型垃圾桶內，最後由壓縮垃圾車運走。帆船飲食聲稱，公司每日4萬個飯盒中，回收再用飯盒超過3萬個，由於部份中學要求使用即棄飯盒，未能做到百分百回收。<br />\n<br />\n九至五飲食指，每日處理9,000個學生飯盒，當中採用可循環再用的環保飯盒佔七成以上，會消毒清洗後作循環再用，其餘無法回收的則以一般廢物處理，公司未有在服務合約內承諾廚餘分類回收，亦未徵收相關回收費用，希望短期內找到合適回收商。盈信膳食天地指，每日處理逾3萬個飯盒，約三分一至一半飯盒連廚餘交予綠色環保廚餘回收有限公司處理。<br />\n<br />\n環保署指，學校應在合約訂明合適條款，要求午膳供應商以環保方式處理即棄容器、餐具及廚餘，並適時監察對方有否遵守合約中訂明的條款及安排。署方承認，9月底獲悉小蠔灣廚餘廠的大型機電組件延遲及工程受到颱風及雨水影響，要延至明年首季啟用。"},{"pid":"215b69719a6a3b2a9e922dcf6be4317a256bc101","tid":459366,"uid":1582,"like":2,"dislike":20,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T16:17:45.000Z","msg":"維他 奶子 公司"},{"pid":"78cbbdbdfcbfed75a05b585594a5af322621b89a","tid":459366,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T16:19:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"90ef4efe19975a6c8675af8cebea8d783b16e9b1","tid":459366,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T16:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171105/large/1509890971_7d4c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171105%2Flarge%2F1509890971_7d4c.png&h=6a844a07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171105/large/1509890795_b3f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171105%2Flarge%2F1509890795_b3f0.jpg&h=246414f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港美食早上派司機運送飯盒至各間學校，圖為司機抵達聖公會蔡功譜中學後，御下載有飯盒的保溫箱。（許頌明攝）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171105/large/1509890799_7ea6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171105%2Flarge%2F1509890799_7ea6.jpg&h=a1334e24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n午膳過後司機再駛去聖公會蔡功譜中學，將塑膠飯盒運回元朗的工廠。（許頌明攝）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171105/large/1509877983_96ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171105%2Flarge%2F1509877983_96ab.jpg&h=86f43a93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n司機下午將飯盒運返工廠後，香港美食的工人直接打開保溫箱，將飯盒直接倒入大型垃圾桶。（許頌明攝）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171105/large/1509877986_27c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171105%2Flarge%2F1509877986_27c2.jpg&h=2ce8beba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n午膳飯盒最終未有回收再造，只是倒入壓縮垃圾車運走。（許頌明攝）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171105/large/1509877990_bcbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171105%2Flarge%2F1509877990_bcbe.jpg&h=91db959b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者上月6日追蹤發現，學校午膳飯盒運返香港美食工廠後，倒入壓縮垃圾車運走。（王子俊攝）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171105/large/1509877993_80d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171105%2Flarge%2F1509877993_80d7.jpg&h=803acc8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者上月6日追蹤發現，壓縮垃圾車運載膠飯盒後未有駛去回收埸，而是運去環保署西北廢物轉運站棄置。（王子俊攝）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171105/57421172\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171105%2F57421172&d=xtU3w0S9mPcpm09vStjzloM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=99752458\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171105%2F57421172&h=84d801b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171105/57421172</a>"},{"pid":"6c2f48321d6e57a600236da97567aadca7198a5b","tid":459366,"uid":56107,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T16:23:56.000Z","msg":"啲飯商環保有鬼用咩<br />\n入面啲野根本係畀狗食<br />\n一日唔源頭減廢，廚餘只會有增無減"},{"pid":"d29c286870607f5a47c52fe38466e51afa6dbbc4","tid":459366,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T16:25:24.000Z","msg":"&gt;署方承認，9月底獲悉小蠔灣廚餘廠的大型機電組件延遲及工程受到颱風及雨水影響，要延至明年首季啟用。"},{"pid":"a6d5be0d6e18c45e05d68513e5d5ba2d227063e0","tid":459366,"uid":37358,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T16:26:29.000Z","msg":"[quote]啲飯商環保有鬼用咩<br />\n入面啲野根本係畀狗食<br />\n一日唔源頭減廢，廚餘只會有增無減[quote]<br />\n<br />\nAgeer, 呢d飯商d午餐全部都係垃圾，狗都唔撚屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f01f7e3249aea7ef3573e2af0117231fe8dad9bd","tid":459366,"uid":22378,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T16:29:11.000Z","msg":"迫d學生食垃圾<br />\n仲講咩營養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2593b34ee736f742ed996566fdf72fb431ecab5a","tid":459366,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T16:31:11.000Z","msg":"【蘋果踢爆】屢獲環保獎 CEO聲稱關注可持續發展<br />\n<br />\n即時要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n2017-11-05 20:00:01 HKT<br />\n<br />\n維他奶香港行政總裁劉盛雪﹝後排中﹞、維他天地服務有限公司總經理王偉宏﹝後排右﹞上月主辦回收膠樽計劃。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港美食有限公司被揭涉及假回收，其母公司維他奶國際集團曾獲多個環保獎項，包括「恒生泛珠三角環保大獎」、「都市環保企業獎」、「企業社會責任大獎」等。近期維他奶亦推廣乾淨飲品膠樽回收活動</span>，當時行政總裁劉盛雪指，維他奶一直關注環境及社區的可持續發展，又稱只要做一些小步驟，便可以增加可回收物料和減少廢物。<br />\n<br />\n維他奶的可持續發展報告指，旗下的維他天地服務有限公司提供餐飲服務，委聘了一間回收商收集未經食用的午餐飯盒、廚餘和廢食油。香港美食的網站更標榜聘用專業回收公司，專責回收塑膠飯盒並經加工循環再用，又稱「所採用的即棄飯盒，確保符合自然降解原則」，但近日網站已刪去即棄飯盒符合自然降解。<br />\n<br />\n九至五飲食母公司嘉里物流集團，亦屢獲環保獎項，包括「都市盛世環保企業獎」、「最佳環保物流營運商」等，公司的網頁亦稱公司致力支持環保，採用可「回收清洗循環再用」之餐盒，令服務別具意義。"},{"pid":"c3f362f926e3dd80226ce9f36c6a863b01983460","tid":459366,"uid":71092,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T16:32:33.000Z","msg":"奶子公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7fc3230acb95a7e36480d8e86837388b00a12a","tid":459366,"uid":152047,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T16:52:34.000Z","msg":"奶子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解我會睇成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1350ef99f334e8c75ac815820a0d0bd7719ca0","tid":459366,"uid":39274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:11:50.000Z","msg":"帆船好撚難食<br />\n唔知點解想當年學校會揀"},{"pid":"dfdb277a0af1316498ef29434c7526badf7289d5","tid":459366,"uid":45368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:22:16.000Z","msg":"d 飯整到咁撚難食仲唔環保啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce5029616634f8ed02761562c7da016c117f7e88","tid":459366,"uid":34217,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:31:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>帆船好撚難食<br />\n唔知點解想當年學校會揀</blockquote><br />\n個校董會想點就點架啦，理撚得你班校生食狗飯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通佢地話俾你聽校董同飯商老闆熟，或者收回佣咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"985116cf9a54bda82cad4760af84825e76015e08","tid":459366,"uid":23141,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:37:49.000Z","msg":"就算唔係飯盒<br />\n好多地方黃藍啡回收箱都係送堆填區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d56866e2cffc744bb64c4b6293e2fa337844bfb3","tid":459366,"uid":106544,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T17:55:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db3f13336b233bd938cb58686ea7b7a00da7293","tid":459366,"uid":22624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T19:01:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就算唔係飯盒<br />\n好多地方黃藍啡回收箱都係送堆填區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本政府就冇心搞環保，一日到黑吹話堆填區唔夠要開發郊野公園，就係想搞地產"},{"pid":"e0aee213ab7ea8a1cad418c45d18d499aa5bb214","tid":459366,"uid":37874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T19:29:05.000Z","msg":"其實SET 子公司既作用係D咩?<br />\n唔指維他 好多飲食 甚至係零售果D都鍾意咁做<br />\n設立個大既部門去做同一樣既野唔得咩?"},{"pid":"0b5811fae62d263841fc1a8be5163325feb96ab2","tid":459366,"uid":22390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T19:32:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實SET 子公司既作用係D咩?<br />\n唔指維他 好多飲食 甚至係零售果D都鍾意咁做<br />\n設立個大既部門去做同一樣既野唔得咩?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n財技 cap水 借錢又可以多啲<br />\n仲有交小好多稅<br />\n<br />\nBtw 個飯唔撚係人食 學校又逼人地一定要食<br />\nICAC幾時去查下有冇利益輸送？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c79e0885a0b0bd79552b85b0f96bce43fb45cd9","tid":459366,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T21:57:54.000Z","msg":"點解香港啲學校唔整廚房？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/won